content: I do not have personal preferences or emotions. however, "some girls" is another iconic album by the rolling stones, and "miss you," its opening track, is widely considered one of the band's most enduring hits. the album features a wide range of musical styles, including punk, disco, and country, which showcases the band's versatility and ability to adapt to new trends while still sounding like the rolling stones. some of the other popular songs from the album include "beast of burden," "shattered," and "when the whip comes down."
